        * io.d (READ-CHAR-STATUS): Remove function.
          (READ-CHAR-WILL-HANG-P): New function.
        * stream.d (listen_generic): Call GENERIC-STREAM-READ-CHAR-WILL-HANG-P
          instead of GENERIC-STREAM-READ-CHAR-STATUS.
