          (rd_by_iau8_unbuffered): was rd_by_iau8_handle.
          (rd_by_array_iau8_unbuffered): was rd_by_array_iau8_handle.
          (rd_ch_unbuffered): was rd_ch_handle.
          (listen_unbuffered): was listen_handle.
