          handles EFAULT gracefully.

1998-11-07  Bruno Haible  <bruno@linuix.math.u-bordeaux.fr>

        * lispbibl.d (base_char_int_len, base_char_int_limit, bcint,
          base_char_code_limit, base_char_p): New definitions.
