	* constobj.d (version): New bytecode version.
	  (old_version): Remove.
	* misc.d (SYS::VERSION): Drop test for O(old_version).
	* package.d (SYS::OLD-MAKE-PACKAGE, SYS::OLD-%IN-PACKAGE,
